messages.message:
Thanks @avi.
• Yes, Intact are clear this is unofficial - we positioned as requiring Instabase Solution Engineering for actual delivery.
• They are looking for more details, notably if auth / security differs from the Converse API. Or trying to gauge if there is anything that would prevent or they need to consider now it's implementation
• We wouldn't include integrations in PoCs (mainly just solution design). Intact are more gathering final materials / assessments this week from users leveraging Converse to determine next steps from here.
